comment_text: Alan Walker's music is always so captivating and The Spectre is no exception. The combination of powerful beats, haunting vocals, and uplifting lyrics make this track a true masterpiece. Parabéns!

comment_text: Here’s my story with this song. Always heard the non-vocal part of the song from random youtube videos, always liked it but never knew what it was called. Had a dream last night and was doing whatever I was doing, but at the very end of the dream before I woke up, this melody came on and I woke up jamming out. Spent all morning trying to hum it into my phone to figure out what it was to no avail. I thought it was a song by thefatrat but was wrong. Decided to get out my dusty violin and figured out how to play it. After a couple tries of playing it into my phone, this song came up. I almost wrote it off because of the vocals, but I barely heard the background music and realized I’d found it. Great journey, great song.
Name: The_Spectre
